               <p>JOHN KLOS. On the 23d of July I was going down the <placeName id="t18280911-169-crimeloc858">Haymarket</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18280911-169-crimeloc858" type="placeName" value="Haymarket"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18280911-169-crimeloc858" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-169-off856 t18280911-169-crimeloc858"></join>; I took out my handkerchief, and put it into my pocket again - in about two minutes after a little boy told me I had lost it; I looked, and saw the prisoner with it in his hand - he ran to Brewer-street, and then to Peter-street, where he was stopped; I never lost sight of him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280911-169-person984">
                  GEORGE 
                  BARRY
               <interp inst="t18280911-169-person984" type="surname" value="BARRY"></interp>
