                     <interp inst="t18280911-169-person984" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was in Brewer-street, and saw the prisoner running, and the prosecutor pursuing, crying Stop thief! - I ran and seized him; he said he would give me the property back, if I would let him go - I took the handkerchief from his pocket.</p>
